# dist/ — Build deliverables
#
# This folder and its subdirectories are kept in git (via .gitkeep)
# so that build.bat can find them on a fresh clone.
# The actual binaries (APK, AAB, EXE, MSI) are NOT committed.
#
# Only .gitignore and .gitkeep files survive in version control.

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Except these tracking files
!.gitignore
!.gitkeep
!**/.gitignore
!**/.gitkeep
